---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contribute - Surf Deeper" description="How to contribute guides and spots using our content system: folders, sections, ordering, and Markdown formatting.">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Contribute</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Share your knowledge, help the community</p>
  </header>

  <section class="contribution-types">
    <h2>How You Can Contribute</h2>
    <div class="contribution-grid">
      <div class="contribution-card">
        <h3>Guides</h3>
        <p>Write Markdown articles in our `guides` collection.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/tree/main/src/content/guides" target="_blank" class="contribute-link">Guides folder</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contribution-card">
        <h3>Sections</h3>
        <p>Lightly manage sections for Guides.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/blob/main/src/content/guides/_sections.json" target="_blank" class="contribute-link">Sections config</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contribution-card">
        <h3>Spots</h3>
        <p>Optional for now ‚Äî brief Markdown spot profiles.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/tree/main/spots" target="_blank" class="contribute-link">Spots folder</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contribution-card">
        <h3>Fix Pin Locations</h3>
        <p>Drag pins on the map to correct spot locations.</p>
        <a href="/maps" class="contribute-link">View Spots Map</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>Update Spot Coordinates</h2>
    <p>If you notice a spot's pin is in the wrong location on the map:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Go to the <a href="/maps">Spots page</a></li>
      <li>Click on the spot marker to open the popup</li>
      <li>Click "üìç Pin in wrong location?"</li>
      <li>Drag the pin to the correct location</li>
      <li>Click "Done - Show Instructions" to get the new coordinates</li>
      <li>Follow the GitHub link to submit your correction</li>
    </ol>
    <p>The coordinates are stored in the frontmatter of each spot's markdown file at <code>src/content/spots/</code>.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>Keep it simple. Follow existing patterns. That‚Äôs it.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Put guides in <code>src/content/guides/&lt;section&gt;/&lt;slug&gt;.md</code></li>
      <li>Frontmatter: <code>title</code> (required), <code>description</code> and <code>order</code> (optional)</li>
      <li>Sections = folder names; display labels and order live in <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/blob/main/src/content/guides/_sections.json" target="_blank">_sections.json</a></li>
      <li>Sorting: by <code>order</code>, then by <code>title</code></li>
    </ul>

    <p>Schema lives in <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/blob/main/src/content/config.ts" target="_blank">content config</a>. Browse existing files in the <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/tree/main/src/content/guides" target="_blank">guides folder</a> and copy the closest example.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>Quick steps</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the <a href="https://github.com/surfdeeper/surfdeeper/tree/main/src/content/guides" target="_blank">guides folder</a>.</li>
      <li>Copy an existing file in the right section; rename with a clear slug.</li>
      <li>Edit the <code>title</code> and content; add <code>order</code> if you want to control position.</li>
      <li>Open a PR. We‚Äôll review quickly.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="article">
    <h2>PR workflow (short)</h2>
    <p>Use the GitHub UI for quick edits, or develop locally with <code>npm run dev</code>. Keep changes small and follow existing patterns. Link sources when helpful.</p>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #00ff88;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .contribution-types h2,
  .article h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff88;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contribution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contribution-card {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contribution-card:hover {
    border-color: #00ff88;
  }

  .contribution-card h3 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contribution-card p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .contribution-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contribution-card li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .contribution-card li::before {
    content: "‚Üí";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00cc6a;
  }

  .contribute-link {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #00ff88;
    color: #0f172a;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contribute-link:hover {
    background-color: #00cc6a;
  }

  .article {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .article p, .article li {
    color: #00ff88;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }
  .article ul, .article ol {
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  /* remove extra cardy blocks */

  .github-contribution {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .templates .code-block {
    display: block;
    background: #0f172a;
    color: #d1fae5;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
  }

  .github-contribution h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .github-contribution p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contribution-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step-card {
    background-color: #0f172a;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    border-color: #00ff88;
  }

  .step-card h3 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step-card p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .step-card a {
    color: #00cc6a;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .step-card a:hover {
    color: #00ff88;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-method h4 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method p {
    color: #00ff88;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
